Or what are some of those best
practices for tablets that

00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:13.180
make it so much better on
a tablet and a different

00:10:13.180 --> 00:10:14.840
experience from the
mobile device?

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:15.130
RETO MEIER: Right.

00:10:15.130 --> 00:10:15.400
OK.

00:10:15.400 --> 00:10:15.670
Yeah.

00:10:15.670 --> 00:10:16.380
And that's excellent.

